Install in "~/Library/Services"

How to use: Once installed, "Encrypt Selected" will appear in the
Right-click context menu. 

You will be prompted for a password, the selection will be encrypted in
a new disk-image and sent to the "Trash".

!IMPORTANT NOTE: You must empty the trash before the contents are really
gone!

To Securely Erase the Trash Folder, Hold the Command key while
Right-Clicking it to erase everything inside forever!
